                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00B/597: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-06-14T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 14, 1929—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>195. Newspaper reports state that Soviets have been mobilizing forces on
                    Chinese-Siberian border. Can you confirm?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clark</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
